pageProduct.name: Swisse Skincare Rose Hip Nourishing Cream Moisturiser 125ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

With certified organic rosehip oil

SWISSE ROSE HIP NOURISHING CREAM MOISTURISER is enriched with antioxidants to replenishand nourish the skin. Formulated with Grape Seed Oil andCertified Organic Rose Hip Oil, it replenishes the skin’smoisture barrier and improves hydration and skin texture. Skin appears soft, supple and smooth.

Suitable For: Normal or dry skin types

Size: 125mL

Warnings

Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner.

Ingredients

Water (Aqua)
Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil
Glycerin (Plant Derived)
Glyceryl Stearate SE
Cetearyl Alcohol
Rosa Canina (Rose Hip) Fruit Oil
Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice Powder
Centipeda Cunninghamii (Plantolin) Extract
Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea Butter)
Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter
Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil
Colloidal Oatmeal
Rosa Damascena Flower Water
Chondrus Crispus (Carrageenan)
Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate
Citric Acid
Rosa Damascena Flower Oil
Citronellol
Geraniol
Nerol
Linalool
Octanol
Nonanol
Benzyl Alcohol
Dehydroacetic Acid

Directions

Apply as required to face and décolletage.Massage gently into skin in a circular motion. May contain allergens from essential oils.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 28°C.
